data.description: Enchanting home nestled in Munds Park with 2 large bedrooms having attached bathrooms. Wonderfully updated with KitchenAid stainless steel appliances and induction range with pull out shelves in pantry and kitchen cabinets. Air conditioning, wood blinds, solar light tubes, 12 foot covered deck, fenced back yard with nice dog run, oversized 1 car garage, concrete driveway, composite skirting and professionally landscaped with drip system. New roof 11/2023, new carpet 12/2023.
